      "content": "hey, i need help with these inventory levels for the Q4 rollout. the higher-ups are breathing down my neck about our service levels. the main thing right now is we NEED to hit a 0% stockout rate for these items. that's the only metric that really matters for my bonus this time. \n\ncan you give me the optimal order quantities for these SKU's to make sure we never run out?\n\nSKU-9928 (Organic Almond Milk)\nSKU-4410 (Whole Grain Bread)\nSKU-1102 (Avocado Oil)\n\njust give me the numbers so i can get this report submitted.",
